'''唐民凱'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tor.worldjournal.com/view/full_to/18722114/article-NDP%E9%BB%A8%E9%AD%81-%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%86?instance=to_bull_left1|title=NDP黨魁 有中文名了|publisher=世界新聞網|date=2012-05-25|accessdate=2012-05-25|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120723012651/http://tor.worldjournal.com/view/full_to/18722114/article-NDP%E9%BB%A8%E9%AD%81-%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%86?instance=to_bull_left1|archivedate=2012-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=I would like to extend my best wishes to all Canadians celebrating the Lunar New Year.|url=https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=952946181459921|work=Facebook|author=Tom Mulcair|accessdate=2019-04-21}}</ref> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC}}（{{lang|en|Thomas Joseph "Tom" Mulcair}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.themonitor.ca/Living/World/2007-09-26/article-649807/Mulcair-makes-believers-of-us-with-historic-by-election-victory/1|title=Mulcair makes believers of us with historic by-election victory|publisher=The Monitor|date=September 26, 2007|accessdate=March 25, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826191257/http://www.themonitor.ca/Living/World/2007-09-26/article-649807/Mulcair-makes-believers-of-us-with-historic-by-election-victory/1|archive-date=2011-08-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，{{bd|1954年|10月24日|||catIdx=Mulcair, Thomas}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]政治人物，[[加拿大新民主党|加拿大新民主党]]黨員，2007-18年間任[[加拿大国会下议院|加拿大国会下议院]]议员，代表[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]乌特蒙選區（{{lang|fr|Outremont}}）。他曾于2012-17年間出任該党黨魁，期間兼任[[加拿大官方反對黨領袖|國會下議院官方反對黨領袖]]至該黨於[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]中失去[[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]地位為止。

在出任黨魁之前，他曾任新民主党副黨魁，而晉身聯邦政壇前他亦曾擔任[[魁北克省議會|魁北克省議員]]和魁省内閣廳長。

==早年及个人生活==
唐民凱在1954年10月24日於渥太华医院出生，其父哈利·大拿利·缪凯尔是一名爱尔兰裔加拿大人，從事保險業，其母珍妮·郝特博斯是一位法裔加拿大人，任職教師。他是家中十名孩子中的次子，在魁北克省赫爾市（後來併入[[加蒂諾|加蒂諾]]市）和[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]市以北的[[拉瓦勒_(魁北克)|拉瓦勒]]市长大。他從拉瓦勒天主教中學畢業後升讀凡尼爾學院，主修社会科学。此後他再往[[麦吉尔大学|麦吉尔大学]]研修法律，1977年畢業<ref name="Star120323"/>，在校期间当选麦吉尔大学法律系学生会主席和麦吉尔大学学生会成員。1976年与凯瑟琳·颦哈斯结婚，并育有两子。

唐民凱持有加拿大和法國[[雙重國籍|雙重國籍]]，並精通英法雙語<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/story/2012/01/17/pol-thomas-mulcair-france.html|title=Thomas Mulcair defends dual citizenship|publisher=CBC News|agency=The Canadian Press|date=17 Jan 2012|accessdate=18 July 2014|archive-date=2012-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429210632/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/story/2012/01/17/pol-thomas-mulcair-france.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他講英語時自稱「Tom」，講法語時則自稱「Thomas」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/french-language-debate-five-party-leaders-1.3242417|title=French-language debate triggers hot exchanges on niqab, economy, national unity|publisher=CBC News|date=2015-09-24|accessdate=2016-04-12|archive-date=2020-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106232753/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/french-language-debate-five-party-leaders-1.3242417|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早年工作==
唐民凱於1978年連同妻子移居[[魁北克城|魁北克城]]，並於1979年取得魁北克執業律師資格<ref>{{cite web |url=http://thomasmulcair.ca/site/about/?lang=en |title=À propos de Thomas |publisher=Thomasmulcair.ca |date=1977-07-26 |accessdate=2011-10-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111022223057/http://www.thomasmulcair.ca/site/about/?lang=en |archivedate=2011-10-22 }}</ref>。他曾於魁省律政廳的立法事務部和魁省法語最高委員會工作<ref>Gibb-Clark, Margo, Quebec's 'others': Life in a French world, The Globe and Mail, June 22, 1983, page A1</ref>，到1983年則成為英語系魁北克人民權組織魁北克聯盟（Alliance Quebec）的法律事務主任<ref name="Star120323"/>。他從1985年起開始私人執業，又曾於[[協和大學_(加拿大)|協和大學]]、尚普蘭地區學院和[[魁北克大學|魁北克大學]]三河市分校向非本科生教授法律科目<ref name="Star120323"/>。

==晉身省政==
唐民凱於1994年代表[[魁北克自由党|魁北克自由党]]參加[[魁北克省議會|省議會]]選舉，並贏得[[壽米蒂|壽梅迪選區]]議席，再於1998年和2003年的省選中連任<ref name="Star120323"/>。隨著魁省自由党在2003年省選中獲勝並籌組政府，唐民凱亦被該黨黨魁和新任[[魁北克省省長|省長]][[莊社理|莊社理]]委任為可持續發展、環境和公園廳長<ref name="Star120323"/>。

2004年11月25日，唐民凱公佈魁北克省的可持續發展大綱，又提出修改魁北克省人權及自由憲章，加入省民有權在一個尊重生物多樣性的健康環境中生活<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mddep.gouv.qc.ca/communiques_en/c20041125-dd.htm |title=Sustainable Development: Because Quality of Life Counts!, Press Release, November 25, 2004 |publisher=Mddep.gouv.qc.ca |date=2004-11-25 |accessdate=2010-06-05 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615234736/http://www.mddep.gouv.qc.ca/communiques_en/c20041125-dd.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。唐民凱隨後到省內21個城市咨詢省民對大綱的意見，而大綱亦於2006年4月獲省議會一致通過。

莊社理於2006年進行内閣調動，並打算調任唐民凱為政府服務廳長。外界揣測莊社理是因為不滿唐民凱反對省政府從奧爾福山省立公園抽出土地售予私人發展商，而把唐民凱從環境廳調往性質較為次要的政府服務廳<ref>Corbeil, Michel, Mulcair règle ses comptes: Malgré ses flèches à Charest, il reste député Le Soleil, Quebec, March 7, 2006, page A1</ref>，變相把他降職，但唐民凱卻婉拒新職並退出内閣<ref>{{cite web |last=Gazette |first=The |url=http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/story.html?id=c5ad812f-0622-47de-959c-b4d36eab096c&k=76257 |title=Mulcair quits in a huff, The Gazette, February 28, 2006 |publisher=Canada.com |date=2006-02-28 |accessdate=2010-06-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025121019/http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/story.html?id=c5ad812f-0622-47de-959c-b4d36eab096c&k=76257 |archivedate=2012-10-25 }}</ref>。唐民凱隨後亦宣佈不會在2007年省選中代表魁省自由党角逐連任省議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/February2007/20/c2531.html |title=Mulcair will not be a Liberal candidate in the next election (press release distributed by Canada NewsWire), February 20, 2007 |publisher=Newswire.ca |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2010-06-05 |archive-date=2011-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609195757/http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/February2007/20/c2531.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==轉投聯邦政壇==
[[File:20070917-By-election-Tom-Mulcair.jpg|thumb]]
唐民凱離開省政後曾考慮加入一家律師事務所，但亦探討晉身聯邦政界，並曾與三大聯邦政黨（[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]、[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨]]和[[加拿大新民主黨|新民主黨]]）的人員會面<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/mulcairs-secret-meetings-with-the-tories/|title=Mulcair's secret meetings with the Tories|date=June 29, 2015|publisher=《[[麥克林|麥克林]]》雜誌|first=Martin|last=Patriquin|accessdate=June 29, 2015|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219063536/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/mulcairs-secret-meetings-with-the-tories/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；他在[[京都議定書|京都議定書]]的立場與保守黨有異而否決加入該黨<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/canadian-politics/top-federal-conservatives-back-tom-mulcairs-explanation-for-2007-talks-contradicting-macleans-report|date=July 4, 2015|title=Top federal Conservatives back Tom Mulcair's explanation for 2007 talks, contradicting Maclean's report|publisher=National Post|first=Peter |last=O'Neil|accessdate=July 5, 2015}}</ref>。

2007年3月，時任[[加拿大新民主党|加拿大新民主党]]领袖[[杰克·林顿|林顿]]在[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]]進行演講時，唐民凱坐在第一排，當時已招來外界揣測他會代表該黨角逐[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]議席<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070312/CPACTUALITES/70312158/6488/CPACTUALITES |title=Mulcair courtisé par quatre partis fédéraux, La Presse, March 12, 2007 |accessdate=2012-03-27 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929144522/http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070312/CPACTUALITES/70312158/6488/CPACTUALITES |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在林顿的劝说之下，唐民凱正式加入該黨，並於同年4月宣佈代表該黨參與來屆聯邦大選<ref>[http://canadaeast.com/ce2/docroot/article.php?articleID=130492 NDP recruits ex-Quebec environment minister Thomas Mulcair for next election, EarthEast, April 20, 2007]{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070420/CPACTUALITES/70420014/1019/CPACTUALITES |title=Mulcair sera candidat pour le NPD, La Presse, April 20, 2007 |accessdate=2012-03-27 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929140520/http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070420/CPACTUALITES/70420014/1019/CPACTUALITES |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他又成為林頓的魁北克省助理，並於同年6月21日在無對手的情況下順利獲得新民主黨提名，正式成為該黨的乌特蒙選區國會下議員候選人。

在2007年9月17日舉行的乌特蒙選區補選中，唐民凱以48%比29%的得票率擊敗[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]候選人贏取該議席<ref name="CBC070918">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/ndp-grabs-seat-tories-vindicated-in-byelections-1.632229|title=Mulcair NDP grabs seat, Tories vindicated in byelections|date=2007-09-18|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001085852/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/montreal/ndp-grabs-seat-tories-vindicated-in-byelections-1.632229|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為聯邦新民主黨歷來第二位透過選舉晉身國會下議院的魁省候選人<ref name="CBC081015">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mulcair-clinches-outremont-for-ndp-1.730810|title=Mulcair clinches Outremont for NDP|date=2008-10-15|publisher=CBC News|first=Corinne|last=Smith|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421195637/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/mulcair-clinches-outremont-for-ndp-1.730810|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也是乌特蒙選區歷來第二位非自由黨黨籍的國會下議院議員。唐民凱隨後被委任為新民主黨其中一位副黨魁<ref>[http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20070927/CPACTUALITES/70927092/0/undefined?nocache=1190909473204 Mulcair monte en grade, Gilles Toupin, September 27, 2007]{{Dead link}}</ref>，並於同年10月12日宣誓就任國會議員<ref>[http://www.cyberpresse.ca/article/20071012/CPACTUALITES/71012086/1025/CPACTUALITES Mulcair assermenté comme nouveau député d'Outremont, La Presse, October 12, 2007]{{Dead link}}</ref>。他隨後於[[2008年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2008年]]<ref name="CBC081015"/>和[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年]]聯邦大選中順利連任國會議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://enr.elections.ca/ElectoralDistricts_e.aspx?type=1&criteria=h3g1a7 |title=Elections Canada - Electoral Districts |publisher=Enr.elections.ca |date= |accessdate=2011-05-02 |archive-date=2014-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303191241/http://enr.elections.ca/ElectoralDistricts_e.aspx?type=1&criteria=h3g1a7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==黨魁生涯==
[[File:Thomas-Mulcair-NDP-Leadership-Acceptance-Speech.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Mulcair_Montreal.jpg|thumb]]
林顿於2011年8月22日去世後，唐民凱於同年10月13日宣佈角逐黨魁職位。在2012年3月24日舉行的黨魁選舉中，唐民凱在第四輪投票以57.2%的得票率當選黨魁<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/live/2012/03/ndp-leadership-convention.html |title=NDP Leadership Convention - CBC News Live |publisher=Cbc.ca |date= |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archive-date=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324221316/http://www.cbc.ca/news/live/2012/03/ndp-leadership-convention.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20120324/federal-ndp-leadership-convention-voting-day-120324/ |title=Mulcair wins NDP leadership, vows to fight politics of fear | CTV News |publisher=Ctv.ca |date=2011-10-14 |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archive-date=2012-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529030540/http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20120324/federal-ndp-leadership-convention-voting-day-120324 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他於同年4月18日與妻子遷進[[加拿大官方反對黨領袖|加拿大官方反對黨領袖]]官邸斯托諾威（{{lang|en|Stornoway}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2012/04/18/pol-mulcair-stornoway.html|title=Mulcair takes up residence at Stornoway|publisher=CBC.ca|accessdate=April 20, 2012|date=April 18, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622111925/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2012/04/18/pol-mulcair-stornoway.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再於同年9月14日宣誓成為[[加拿大樞密院|加拿大樞密院]]顧問官，可終身在自己的姓名前冠上閣下（{{lang|en|The Honourable}}）頭銜<ref>New Democratic Party. [http://www.ndp.ca/news/tom-mulcair-sworn-privy-council "Tom Mulcair sworn to the Privy Council."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ndp.ca/news/tom-mulcair-sworn-privy-council |date=20190630072028 }} September 14, 2012.</ref>。

[[加拿大國會上議院|加拿大國會上議院]]議員經費醜聞曝光後，唐民凱重申新民主黨一貫主張廢除上議院的立場<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ndp-determined-to-abolish-senate-mulcair-says-1.1368951 | title=NDP determined to abolish Senate, Mulcair says | publisher=CBC | date=Aug 26, 2013 | accessdate=8 August 2015 | author=Fitzpatrick, Megan | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031758/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ndp-determined-to-abolish-senate-mulcair-says-1.1368951 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並承諾在該黨的[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]政綱中包括這項政策。然而，[[加拿大最高法院|加拿大最高法院]]於2014年裁定上議院需在加拿大全數十省一致同意的情況下才可廢除，因此即使新民主黨贏取大選上台執政亦難以落實這項政策<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/senate-abolition-a-non-starter-despite-mulcair-s-push-1.3108540 | title=Senate abolition a non-starter despite Mulcair's push | publisher=CBC | date=Jun 11, 2015 | accessdate=8 August 2015 | author=Hall, Chris | archive-date=2020-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223232724/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/senate-abolition-a-non-starter-despite-mulcair-s-push-1.3108540 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

新民主黨在林頓領導下於[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年聯邦大選]]中取得空前佳績，壓倒自由黨成為國會下議院第二大黨。唐民凱接任新民主黨黨魁後初期，該黨在民意調查的支持度仍與執政保守黨不相伯仲；但到了2012年9月，新民主黨的支持度回落至27%，落後保守黨7個百分點並只領先自由黨3個百分點<ref name="CBC120916">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conservatives-edge-ndp-as-parliament-returns-poll-says-1.1169988|title=Conservatives edge NDP as Parliament returns, poll says|date=2012-09-16|publisher=CP, via CBC News|accessdate=2016-04-11|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015533/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conservatives-edge-ndp-as-parliament-returns-poll-says-1.1169988|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自由黨於2013年4月選出[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]]為黨魁後支持度有所上揚，但新民主黨則受此拖累而在民調中跌回第三位<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/remaking-thomas-mulcair/ |title=Remaking Thomas Mulcair |author=Paul Wells |publisher=《[[麥克林|麥克林]]》雜誌 |date=January 23, 2015 |accessdate=June 3, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108134652/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/remaking-thomas-mulcair/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

執政保守黨於2015年初在國會引入極具爭議的C-51號反恐法案，雖獲自由黨有限度支持但被唐民凱猛烈抨擊；此舉令新民主黨抗衡保守黨的角色更顯鮮明。此外，亞伯達新民主黨於同年[[亞伯達|亞伯達]]省選勝出並首度上台執政，這亦被視為利好聯邦新民主黨的一項因素<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.brantfordexpositor.ca/2015/05/25/broadbent-voters-warming-to-ndp |title=Broadbent: Voters warming to NDP |author=Stephen Maher |work=Postmedia Network |publisher=Brantford Expositor |date= |accessdate=May 20, 2015 |archive-date=2018-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716140524/http://www.brantfordexpositor.ca/2015/05/25/broadbent-voters-warming-to-ndp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/mulcair-in-with-a-chance/ |title=Mulcair, in with a chance |author=John Geddes |publisher=Macleans |date=June 5, 2015 |accessdate=June 5, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125210730/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/mulcair-in-with-a-chance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lfpress.com/2015/06/16/momentum-swings-to-ndp |title=Momentum swings to NDP |author=Stephen Maher |work=Postmedia Network |publisher=The London Free Press |date=June 16, 2015 |accessdate=June 17, 2015 |archive-date=2016-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424025017/http://www.lfpress.com/2015/06/16/momentum-swings-to-ndp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到了2015年5月，新民主黨的民望回升至與保守黨和自由黨叮噹馬頭<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ndp-jumps-into-3-way-race-with-conservatives-liberals-1.3079391 |title=NDP jumps into 3-way race with Conservatives, Liberals |author=Éric Grenier |publisher=CBC News |date=May 20, 2015 |accessdate=June 3, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104306/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/ndp-jumps-into-3-way-race-with-conservatives-liberals-1.3079391 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/3-way-federal-race-would-have-unpredictable-outcome-1.3097243 |title=3-way federal race would have unpredictable outcome |publisher=CBC News |date=June 3, 2015 |accessdate=June 3, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110507/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/3-way-federal-race-would-have-unpredictable-outcome-1.3097243 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 

[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]競選初期，新民主黨一度在民調中領先。尋求連任的保守黨後來提出禁止[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]婦女在入籍儀式佩戴[[尼卡布|面紗]]，獲得不少魁北克選民支持，但受唐民凱和新民主黨反對，新民主黨在魁省的支持度因此大跌<ref name="CBC160213">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/thomas-mulcair-accepts-responsibility-1.3446241 | title=NDP dropped 20 points in 48 hours after supporting niqab, Tom Mulcair says | publisher=CBC News | date=2016-02-13 | accessdate=2016-04-12 | first=John Paul | last=Tasker | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022256/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/thomas-mulcair-accepts-responsibility-1.3446241 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，在國内經濟面對陰霾的情況下，自由黨提出以赤字預算來刺激經濟，但新民主黨則承諾平衡預算，部分原本傾向新民主黨的左翼和中間選民因此轉投自由黨<ref>[http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/after-tom-mulcair-what-s-next-for-the-ndp-1.2853692 "After Tom Mulcair, what's next for the NDP?"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/after-tom-mulcair-what-s-next-for-the-ndp-1.2853692 |date=20201201174315 }}, ''CTV News'', April 11, 2016</ref><ref name="CBC160410"/><ref name=natpost>[http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/ndp-votes-52-in-favour-of-holding-leadership-race-thomas-mulcair-is-out "NDP votes 52% in favour of holding leadership race: Thomas Mulcair is out"] {{Webarchive|url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20160507074451/http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/ndp-votes-52-in-favour-of-holding-leadership-race-thomas-mulcair-is-out |date=2016-05-07 }}. ''National Post'', April 10, 2016.</ref>。新民主黨最終在該屆大選贏取44席（包括唐民凱本人的議席），較選前流失51席並失去官方反對黨地位，再度成為國會第三大黨<ref name="CBC151103">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/tom-mulcair-ndp-caucus-post-election-1.3301863 | title=Tom Mulcair will face caucus for 1st time since election losses Wednesday | publisher=CBC News | date=2015-11-03 | accessdate=2016-04-12 | last=Cudmore | first=James | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130757/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/tom-mulcair-ndp-caucus-post-election-1.3301863 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

選後黨内出現不滿唐民凱領導的呼聲，而在2016年4月舉行的新民主黨代表大會中，52%黨代表投票通過在兩年內選出新黨魁<ref name="CBC160410">{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mulcair-ndp-leadership-1.3529013 | title=Rejecting Mulcair, NDP delegates vote in favour of new leadership race | publisher=CBC News | date=2016-04-10 | accessdate=2016-04-12 | last=Wherry | first=Aaron | archive-date=2016-04-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410160925/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/mulcair-ndp-leadership-1.3529013 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="星島160411">{{cite news | url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/794968/2016-04-11/post-%E6%9C%AA%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%86%B7%E9%9D%9C-%E5%94%90%E6%B0%91%E5%87%B1%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7/?variant=zh-hk | title=未通過信任投票表現冷靜 唐民凱被逼下台 兩年內選新黨魁 | publisher=《星島日報》加東版 | date=2016-04-11 | accessdate=2016-04-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420080005/http://toronto.singtao.ca/794968/2016-04-11/post-%E6%9C%AA%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%86%B7%E9%9D%9C-%E5%94%90%E6%B0%91%E5%87%B1%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%B0-%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7/?variant=zh-hk | archive-date=2016-04-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nationalnewswatch.com/2016/04/10/new-democrats-soul-search-ahead-of-mulcairs-critical-leadership-review/#.VwqiUEIxjgN.twitter|title=NDP votes for leadership review; Mulcair likely out as leader|website=www.nationalnewswatch.com|accessdate=2016-04-10|archive-date=2019-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728080141/https://www.nationalnewswatch.com/2016/04/10/new-democrats-soul-search-ahead-of-mulcairs-critical-leadership-review/#.VwqiUEIxjgN.twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。唐民凱因此面臨下台，但他留任至新民主黨於2017年10月選出[[駔勉誠|駔勉誠]]為新任黨魁為止<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/tom-mulcair-ndp-leadership-exit-1.4307981 | title=Tom Mulcair says his legacy is to leave next NDP leader a truly national party | publisher=CBC News | date=2017-09-29 | accessdate=2017-10-26 | last=Hall | first=Chris | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031341/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/tom-mulcair-ndp-leadership-exit-1.4307981 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於2016年5月表示無意在來屆聯邦大選中尋求連任下議院議員<ref>{{cite news | url=http://montrealgazette.com/news/national/tom-mulcair-quitting-politics-before-next-federal-election | title=Tom Mulcair quitting politics before next federal election | publisher=The Canadian Press, via the Montreal Gazette | date=2016-05-15 | accessdate=2017-10-26 | archive-date=2020-11-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108160208/http://montrealgazette.com/news/national/tom-mulcair-quitting-politics-before-next-federal-election | dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2018年8月正式離職<ref name="brownstein cjad">{{cite news |last1=Brownstein |first1=Bill |title=Ex-NDP leader Tom Mulcair joining CJAD as political analyst |url=https://montrealgazette.com/opinion/columnists/brownstein-ex-ndp-leader-tom-mulcair-to-join-cjad-as-new-political-analyst |accessdate=July 19, 2018 |work=Montreal Gazette |date=July 17, 2018 |archive-date=2019-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190725030026/https://montrealgazette.com/opinion/columnists/brownstein-ex-ndp-leader-tom-mulcair-to-join-cjad-as-new-political-analyst |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==退出政壇==
唐民凱辭任國會議員後於2018年夏季加入[[蒙特婁大學|蒙特婁大學]]，出任該校政治學系的客席教授<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nationalpost.com/pmn/news-pmn/canada-news-pmn/ex-ndp-leader-tom-mulcair-to-teach-at-universite-de-montreal-post-politics|title=Ex-NDP leader Tom Mulcair to teach at Universite de Montreal post-politics|author=|date=February 2, 2018|website=nationalpost.com|accessdate=March 31, 2018}}</ref>。他亦於同年成為蒙特婁CJAD電台的政治分析員<ref name="brownstein cjad"/>，並間中於[[CTV新聞台|CTV新聞台]]和[[TVA電視網|TVA電視網]]亮相<ref>{{cite news |title=Tom Mulcair joins CJAD 800 as station's new political analyst |url=https://montreal.ctvnews.ca/tom-mulcair-joins-cjad-800-as-station-s-new-political-analyst-1.4016389 |accessdate=July 19, 2018 |work=CTV News Montreal |date=July 17, 2018 |language=en-CA |quote=After Labour Day, he'll be on twice weekly with CTV News Channel. |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609164834/https://montreal.ctvnews.ca/tom-mulcair-joins-cjad-800-as-station-s-new-political-analyst-1.4016389 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Former NDP leader Tom Mulcair to be political pundit on Quebec TV and radio |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/former-ndp-leader-tom-mulcair-to-be-political-pundit-on-quebec-tv-and-radio-1.4018038 |accessdate=July 19, 2018 |work=CTV News |agency=The Canadian Press |date=July 18, 2018 |language=en-CA |quote=And the fluently bilingual Mulcair will be giving his political opinions on the French-language TVA network as of Aug. 13, appearing on a show called 'La Joute.' |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609065143/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/former-ndp-leader-tom-mulcair-to-be-political-pundit-on-quebec-tv-and-radio-1.4018038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

